text=(:title Geist Character Creation:)%0a[[#gtop]]%0a[[GameRef.GeistCharacterCreation?action=edit|Click here to Edit]]%0a%0a%0a(:table border=0 style=float width=40%25 align=right  cellspacing=0 :)%0a(:cellnr align=center:)%0a(:cellnr:)%0a(:cellnr bgcolor=#70b0ca align=center:)%0a'''Contents'''%0a(:cellnr:) %0a*[[#Restricted| Restricted & Banned Items]]%0a*[[#Requirements| Character Requirements ]]%0a*[[#Incentive| Incentive XP ]]%0a*[[#General| General Matters ]]%0a(:tableend:)%0a%0aUnless explicitly stated or claimed here, the character creation rules for Wanton Wicked 3.0 overal take precedence.\\%0a%0a%0a[[#Restricted]]%0a%25color=#70b0ca%25[++'''Restricted & Banned Items'''++]\\%0a%0a• Psyche 3 is 1 slot restricted at creation. 4+ is banned.\\%0a• 3 keys is a restricted slot. 4+ keys are banned at creation.\\%0a• Stygian Key is banned at Creation. Pit Manifestations are 1-slot restricted.\\%0a• Memorabilia are two restricted slots at creation and is very much suggested to have a significant tie-in with the character/Geist.\\%0a• Deathmasks banned.\\%0a%0a[--%25color=#70b0ca%25[[#gtop| Back to top]]--]%0a%0a%0a[[#Requirements]]%0a%25color=#70b0ca%25[++'''Character Requirements'''++]\\%0a%0a'''The following are requirements along with the character sheet at time of consideration for sanctioning and should be worked into the history:'''\\%0a\\%0a• Life before death.\\%0a• What their ‘gift’ was that made them special to the Geist?\\%0a• How did they die?\\%0a• Who their Geist is and why did it chose them?\\%0a• Your character’s Keystone (What is it? Why is it special to the Geist? Etc.)\\%0a• How do you fulfill your Archetype? (‘How are you a Mourner?’)\\%0a%0a[--%25color=#70b0ca%25[[#gtop| Back to top]]--]%0a%0a[[#Incentive]]%0a%25color=#70b0ca%25[++'''Incentive XP'''++]\\%0a%0a%0a%0a[--%25color=#70b0ca%25[[#gtop| Back to top]]--]%0a%0a%0a[[#General]]%0a%25color=#70b0ca%25[++'''General Matters'''++]\\%0a%0a• No specific knowledge of other Supernatural creatures and/or PCs allowed beyond what your [[OccultLore|Occult skill]] indicates. Ghosts are excluded from this.\\%0a• There is no such thing as Status: Underworld. You can involve yourself in the court of a specific Kerberos’ and win Status in a particular Domain, but there is no umbrella Status for the land of the dead.\\%0a• If you have a Haunt at creation, please do explain that as well (What made it a Haunt, is there anything special the staff should know about it to make its history interesting for you, etc.). Simply, ‘This building my character knows about where there’s like some ghosts or whatever’ probably won’t do.\\%0a%0a[--%25color=#70b0ca%25[[#gtop| Back to top]]--]%0a%0a[[#General]]%0a%25color=#70b0ca%25[++'''Ceremonies'''++]\\%0a%0a• Ceremonies are to be reviewed by a case by case basis. 3+ ceremonies counts as 1 restricted slot. 4+ is banned at creation. The best way to give yourself the highest chance of approval, is the make sure the ceremony fits your concept, background, and theme.\\%0a%0a[--%25color=#70b0ca%25[[#gtop| Back to top]]--]%0a\\%0a\\%0a%0a(:include CityBook.GeistNavigationBar:)
